1 721 811 721 811</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n."},{"pid":"20f4a08ca084f7f0778b7d49619509dd004387f4","tid":1453510,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港需要人道救援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下，香港極需要不受滋擾的中立醫療團隊。我們需要無國界醫生、聯合國維和部隊，以及其他人道救援組織。只有他們可以為香港提供正常醫療保障，免於中共香港警察滋擾。以下這個聯署，是要求美國派遣醫療船以提供中立的醫療服務。美國醫療船扺達後，其他國際醫療組織就更易來港協助，以減低香港人在今次戰爭的傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n這是十分實際的要求，也是極為急切和重要。為免香港發生大規模人道災難，請各位簽署並廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=fc9461c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a>"},{"pid":"d6837000f797e1f329b9d769833692d51ea1839f","tid":1453510,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d8ee3a5a968220e05f250a8a2f8704eef2303c","tid":1453510,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721 811 721 811  721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811  721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811 721 811</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac41a81049265dbc6a4a502371ef396776ab423d","tid":1453510,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"坐緊車呀"},{"pid":"6acd4c4e1fa6051deb96bfdc02cf0b16dbcc585e","tid":1453510,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime